casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Fant, Appellant, v. Enright, Clerk, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Fant v. Enright (1994), 68 Ohio St.3d 505.]

(No. 93-2206 Submitted February 22, 1994 Decided March 23, 1994.) Henry J. Fant, pro se. *506Michael Miller, Franklin County Prosecuting Attorney, and Jeffrey L. Glasgow, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
